column5: Here you go for all chocolate moose lovers.Had good drive today.We are going to crash in Eau Clair tonight.We got a few things in the grocery store and can't beleive the prices.Definatly cheaper shopping in Canada with Cdn dollars to boot

If I would have known you were going to be in Eau Clair I would drove up and taken you n Silvia to dinner,could have had some big arse ribeyes somewhere there.have a safe drive tomorrow we have winter storm warning for my are tonight.
